snippet.title: Azutama [あずたま] Game Sample - PC/Doujin
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: January 30, 2010

An old, cute imitation of one of my favorite Japanese oldies, Battle City, but with Azumanga Daioh characters and snowball fighting... and boss characters in cars and people who wear more clothes to resist being knocked out by snowballs. It's nothing too special.
